Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan has taught our African gray parrot to say, I'm calling my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling my lawyer, the bird says.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a practical question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if it would be in the highest good for me to go to school to study Chinese medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to study Chinese medicine for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a drawing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also am a perpetual student, and I don't know if that's pathological or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm just wondering if it would be in my highest good to go to school and study that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, I have a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in his highest good to study Chinese medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And would you mind checking a school that I have in mind, if it's best?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fudan Pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The place he wants to go is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You betcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that on the front there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what I look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say that's me, I'll think of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything is God, if all of us, omnipresent and omnipotent, what is the purpose of God experiencing itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the human notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A hemlock tree does not grow in order to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It grows because it's a hemlock tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's designed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me, why is God like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is God like God?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is God like God?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you're looking for human rationality where it's not really appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody likes to presume that God has human notions and motives and that's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ocean isn't there just so you can swim in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean is there because that's what an ocean is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, there's subject, object, and verb, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,God does this in order to do that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's trying to put it in within a human dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned the quality of intense prayer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My priest, many months ago, gave me this rosary as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I came, I had it for many months,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and before I came to Sedona this weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I had never said a rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So yesterday, at the Chapel of the Holy Cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I dedicated my first rosary to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wept the entire time, and then said three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to thank you for this inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You enjoyed the Chapel of the Holy Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I loved that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the world found out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at three or four in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,usually the traffic dies out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be open all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do they lock it at night now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it used to be open all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and you could go in there and just sit anytime you wanted to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't have mentioned it so many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have kept it to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Loud mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A good place to find solitude is Times Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can spend years there and nobody says hello to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is for you, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, I just wanted to thank you for being such a rich blessing in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't express it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I have contributed to your happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then that makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that your happiness made me happy should make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Befuddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Befuddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that word, befuddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Befuddled brings about befuddlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Befuddlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Befuddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Master In March, you have prayed for me to continue to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By virtue of that, I could come here again without troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All circumstances have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,different from my reptile reptile the look of the face is different left and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,right in daily life my left one is always healthy smiling and strong but my
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,right right part is depressed weak exhausted yeah become easily becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,sad embarrassed and when I meditate sometimes my whole body gets lightened
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,except to my right part of my head except for what he seems to feel like is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,right everything his whole body becomes enlightened but the right side of his
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,head you know like there's a block there oh no get light in the whole body get
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,lightened except yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And on meditation, it seems like dark clouds start from this part
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and spread, veil my whole head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels like the left part of his face is happy, working,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the right part is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's an uncommon condition, but it has a name, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. When he meditates, he feels like this, the right part,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is where the darkness comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything else, he feels, becomes enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's this dark spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's just a natural phenomenon with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So what could he do to change that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he want to change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he would like to have that feeling all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In his body, rather than just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean my right foot should always feel the same as my left foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So what could that represent, then, that he has that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessarily significant or meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My right eye is considerably different than my left eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's just the way it is, the way the retina is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just accept nature how it is, and how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please bless on myself, on my patients, and on my practices?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a blessing to have more patients and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And on her practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs a blessing on her practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to bless your practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bless all your patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do to be the best doctor you can be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do to be the best doctor you can be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you pray for your patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the best you can because you know you're karmically responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And every patient I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw many for 50 years, thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Every patient, what to me was that God's intention was for me to be as helpful as I could to this patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found it very fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I only gave a practice because I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd still be seeing patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But the malpractice insurance became so expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was spending all my time just working for the insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, reluctantly, I just had to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really missed it because it's very gratifying to be able to help people and to relieve suffering and bring forth their gift to the world, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I missed the practice of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And also the fact that with psychiatry, you gave it another dimension besides just the physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you hold my hand for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I miss my old patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't quit until the last one died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I'll stay in practice as long as they're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in his 90s and he teetered in and fell over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well, God, I guess I can retire now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to leave the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally he died, and so I was relieved that I could close my practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, where did all these books come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I ask for your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And second, my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In your work, I've read that love is innate to the capital S self from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That its quality is divinity, which radiates love towards all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that I tend to treat love as if it's some sort of currency
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes from one person to the other, that it comes from an external source.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with anything else out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The way that you walk through the woods, it's your way of being with the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,being with the trees, being with the rabbits, to radiate appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So love has many forms other than affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be appreciation and acknowledgement of the significance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and beauty of the existence of the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got three kitties at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I have a doggie who is also divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you suggest I get a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you suggest getting a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gives love, then he expects love in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So he hasn't learned to give up without...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the doggie sits next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at the doggie, and if I look at the doggie, her tail starts going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't touched her, I haven't spoken to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can feel the love for the dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the doggie's tail starts to wag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the way to be in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that all the people around you are wagging their tails that you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want it drying out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you want it with or without a waggy tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A waggy tail, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the waggy tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your waggy tail picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In my home, I'm trying to have aesthetics,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but a portion of the home has a lot of clutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that indicative of something on the spiritual path?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's significant that part of your house is cluttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm stuck in something with my partner and myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know if you have any insights what the clutter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what it would take to move that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or what could be underlying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or what could be underlying it, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Laziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes time, thought, and energy to clear up clutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're too lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying in bed sleeping when you should be clearing up clutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it indicative of anything in the relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That we're both doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just laziness on both parts, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, clutter is part of the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, work on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you work on it, it won't have clutter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Clutter is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell yourself clutter is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What I do is I confine my clutter to certain areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So like this table from here to there, this can be clutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is not clutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my question is pornography.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How do people overcome pornography?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How do people what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pornography.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Overcome it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shock treatment, how's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, castration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What about something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with castration?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there other options?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Deconditioning yourself, which takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's also just a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't just pornography.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pornography habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the fixation on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't find it's boring after a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have relapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like for four months I would not do anything and then I relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the last sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He said four months he would not do anything and then he'd have a relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'd be like AA, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you give it up one day at a time, which is the only way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
