Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.65,0:58:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about raising levels of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.67,0:58:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.40,0:58:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.34,0:58:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit back a little bit, because that will pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.78,0:58:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Sometimes when
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.82,0:58:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to a beautiful piece
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.92,0:58:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of music, or I'm performing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.65,0:58:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a beautiful piece of music, or I'm praying
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.88,0:58:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to God, I feel these very intense
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.07,0:58:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,feelings of love and bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.98,0:58:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if when I feel those kinds
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.92,0:58:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of feelings, if that is raising my
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.90,0:58:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level, and if so,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.15,0:58:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is just a temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.57,0:58:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rise of a consciousness level,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.65,0:58:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or is that just feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.90,0:58:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.82,0:58:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.46,0:58:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know if
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.00,0:58:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever she listens to a beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.55,0:58:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,piece of music, she feels her
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.00,0:58:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.26,0:58:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,level rising. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.40,0:58:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it just temporary,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.57,0:58:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it actually? Yeah, it's temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.48,0:58:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it actually rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.05,0:58:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it actually raising my consciousness level?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.15,0:58:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that just told me that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.78,0:59:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, praying and listening
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.34,0:59:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to music raises consciousness level?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.67,0:59:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would praying
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.11,0:59:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and listening to music raise your
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.61,0:59:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.07,0:59:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People have been doing that for thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.17,0:59:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of years. And would that be
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.80,0:59:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the way that someone would
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.09,0:59:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to write a work that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.71,0:59:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates higher than they themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.57,0:59:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate? Maybe I didn't hear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.01,0:59:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it right. Did you say that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.86,0:59:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone has a very
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.78,0:59:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,high experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.76,0:59:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.76,0:59:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that they can write a work
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.86,0:59:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about that, and it would calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.00,0:59:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.88,0:59:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other end,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.17,0:59:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if they can't live,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.84,0:59:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,walk the walk, or talk the talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.90,0:59:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then they will not remain
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.90,0:59:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there in that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.40,0:59:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.34,0:59:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.34,0:59:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be loving towards all
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.48,0:59:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,beings, and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.05,1:00:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,not think negatively
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.50,1:00:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of those fumbling idiots.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.15,1:00:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, keeping...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.96,1:00:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a good way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.03,1:00:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.88,1:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.61,1:00:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.80,1:00:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.07,1:00:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.65,1:00:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.65,1:00:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.53,1:01:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask about
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.76,1:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's such thing as
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.80,1:01:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,original sin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.78,1:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing as original sin?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.59,1:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.11,1:01:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,original sin, sweetheart. That's
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.53,1:01:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of religious
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.01,1:01:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,belief system.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.30,1:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there was nobody around,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.88,1:01:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so where would the sin originate
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.07,1:01:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.75,1:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.46,1:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,she would like your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.21,1:01:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.51,1:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.21,1:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.26,1:01:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.61,1:01:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Original sin is a whole big dissertation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.71,1:01:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take me an hour to explain it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.82,1:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? Is somebody here?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.11,1:02:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.55,1:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work. It's helped me a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.94,1:02:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,personally and professionally.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.38,1:02:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for getting him to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.59,1:02:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.71,1:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in southwest Georgia,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.36,1:02:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know you've already
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.84,1:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,spoken some about practices
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.63,1:02:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,today, but I wanted to ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.82,1:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you had any
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.59,1:02:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual or practical advice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.07,1:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still got a lot of years
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.96,1:02:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead of me, assuming the world doesn't end today,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.28,1:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's after 3 o'clock, so I think
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.78,1:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably not going to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.53,1:02:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.84,1:02:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,suggestions for someone
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.90,1:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,practicing in psychiatry now?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.11,1:02:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're practicing psychiatry?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.44,1:02:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You need God's help around
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.94,1:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.44,1:02:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.00,1:02:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was always thankful
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.44,1:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.11,1:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was a greater
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.11,1:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension than just the physical
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.00,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,body. I can include
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.36,1:03:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the person and their personhood
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.44,1:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.84,1:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,appreciate them as
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.44,1:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a being, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.55,1:03:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had some wonderfully
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.11,1:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting patients over the years
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.19,1:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we had a very positive
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.00,1:03:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,transference and
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.21,1:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,counter-transference.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.36,1:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look forward to seeing them
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.09,1:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of them asked me for a picture of myself
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.17,1:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang on the wall because every time he looked
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.17,1:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,at it, he felt better.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.05,1:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And a couple of patients
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.84,1:03:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,were very old and they'd been
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.19,1:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with me for many years
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.51,1:03:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I did not retire until they died.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.82,1:03:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'll
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.78,1:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stay with them to the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.76,1:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.50,1:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of the patients I had,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.23,1:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved, not in a personal
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.94,1:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,way, but I loved
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.57,1:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.61,1:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.80,1:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato chips? No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.82,1:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What doc
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.76,1:04:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't tell you is that a lot of the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.46,1:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,patients couldn't afford the fees and he would
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.48,1:04:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,see them for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.94,1:04:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Free coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.76,1:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They would bring him coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.11,1:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for the bill. They'd bring me coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.69,1:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.03,1:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.71,1:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,have to buy coffee for a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.94,1:05:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we sign all these?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.42,1:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, if they didn't have money,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.32,1:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say I'd see them
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.55,1:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.19,1:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.05,1:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for being my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.42,1:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a study group that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.03,1:05:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,meets at our house.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.76,1:05:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where study group that he
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.07,1:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,lives in Plainto, Texas, and he is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.03,1:05:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a study Plano meets at
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.21,1:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,his house. Oh, yes. We have a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.48,1:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of people from Plano. Yes. Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.82,1:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We asked for your
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.63,1:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,blessings. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.59,1:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.67,1:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we got a number of people from Plano.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.65,1:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people do we have in our
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.88,1:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,study group? It varies
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.96,1:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,between. We had 15
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.07,1:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the beginning, then it goes
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.96,1:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,up and down. Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.76,1:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. It's a great blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.11,1:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teaching is so wonderful. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.63,1:06:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Plano Texas, right? The path is long,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.84,1:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so we ask for your continued blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.94,1:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh. Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.15,1:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.98,1:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,May we have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.61,1:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.53,1:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a photo?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.28,1:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.32,1:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.15,1:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your hand? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.98,1:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.51,1:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless my arm,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.73,1:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,please. Bless my arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.82,1:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, I ask for thy
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.96,1:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,blessing. Dear thy love.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.11,1:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.26,1:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.80,1:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.21,1:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.40,1:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She asks for your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.13,1:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.28,1:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.51,1:07:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.09,1:07:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please me
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.44,1:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a phrase to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.19,1:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.09,1:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please me
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.36,1:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a phrase
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.92,1:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to meditation, meditate
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.98,1:07:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,on specific to me
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.19,1:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.51,1:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplate all my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.17,1:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.38,1:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a mantra that she can
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.80,1:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,use throughout her life,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.55,1:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and we don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.94,1:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never done that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.28,1:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've never done that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.26,1:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.27,1:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.97,1:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray so.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.31,1:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would she do?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.10,1:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What type?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.02,1:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What can she do to, um,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.73,1:08:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that would help her in her
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.35,1:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.25,1:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just meditate
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.88,1:08:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and pray?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.73,1:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just pray and meditate?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.09,1:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pray and meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.75,1:08:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do something special.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.43,1:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, dress up or stand on your head
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.44,1:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or do a dance or anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.77,1:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pray and meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.81,1:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, this and that and the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.21,1:08:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.27,1:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you talk to God in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.02,1:08:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.42,1:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.35,1:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.19,1:09:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, geez.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.38,1:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.22,1:09:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so if you want her to do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.42,1:09:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just, um,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.39,1:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,meditate and then in her mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.73,1:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for the blessings or whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.65,1:09:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that she wants God to help her with.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.92,1:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell God what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.14,1:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.97,1:09:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And what the problem is,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.84,1:09:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and confide in, confide in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.61,1:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.52,1:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.39,1:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.36,1:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pray that it will be okay
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.18,1:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.52,1:09:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But there doesn't have to be anything special to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.53,1:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.38,1:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.81,1:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually you wait till something arises
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.89,1:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that you start doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.93,1:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But then after a while,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.94,1:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you get to be in the habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.14,1:09:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people pray in the morning when they get up
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.01,1:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and they pray at night when they go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.81,1:09:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.97,1:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.06,1:09:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.89,1:09:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She has, she has,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.39,1:09:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.23,1:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She has, she's having a language problem here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.06,1:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.89,1:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pray in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.47,1:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It says to pray in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.88,1:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.72,1:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then pray at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.14,1:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.30,1:10:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So this would help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.27,1:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.11,1:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to talk slow
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.96,1:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because she can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.03,1:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This would help you in your meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.22,1:10:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you get up in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.47,1:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and you, and you pray and meditate,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.85,1:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,say for 20 minutes and then pray and meditate,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.72,1:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,say at night for 20 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.64,1:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that this would help you in, on your path.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.85,1:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.31,1:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.15,1:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.00,1:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my nephew is born just today.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.52,1:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So could you, could you blessing my nephew and his family?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.89,1:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she has, is it your brother or sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.50,1:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger sister, younger brother, younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.15,1:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Her brother just had a baby today.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.92,1:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you bless her nephew?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.07,1:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.22,1:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.42,1:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you send a blessing their way?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.88,1:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The way of whom?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.22,1:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of her new nephew.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.52,1:10:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a new nephew.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.35,1:10:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A new nephew.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.19,1:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even handle the people next door
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.72,1:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you want a new nephew?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.78,1:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete stranger, meaningless to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.52,1:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A good idea, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.56,1:11:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Email us a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.85,1:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have him bless it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.53,1:11:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she has a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.85,1:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.30,1:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, today born.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.11,1:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.96,1:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.56,1:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.39,1:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.35,1:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.88,1:11:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless his little baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.81,1:11:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.07,1:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.73,1:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.73,1:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.34,1:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.18,1:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a picture, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.15,1:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.44,1:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a little tiny thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.56,1:11:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.18,1:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.35,1:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.55,1:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.06,1:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.35,1:12:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless that and pray for it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.30,1:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.97,1:12:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.50,1:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain and weakness under her head before, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.61,1:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask for thy blessing on this left arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.71,1:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.81,1:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.96,1:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for a miracle, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.26,1:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.10,1:12:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.93,1:12:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you for all of your inspiration
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.26,1:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like to have a blessing and a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.56,1:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'd like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.39,1:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing and a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.28,1:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.21,1:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Cracker Jack, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.27,1:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the kid, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.68,1:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep them all laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.36,1:12:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.36,1:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.52,1:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.03,1:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.27,1:13:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.27,1:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to say how deeply grateful we are for your work and your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.50,1:13:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And we love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.46,1:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.75,1:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.75,1:13:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.75,1:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for all you're doing for the population.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.75,1:13:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so great.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.77,1:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.77,1:13:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.06,1:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.06,1:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.06,1:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.42,1:13:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.89,1:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.89,1:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.89,1:13:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.89,1:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.89,1:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.89,1:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.89,1:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.06,1:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.89,1:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.89,1:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.89,1:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.17,1:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.17,1:14:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.09,1:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.09,1:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.09,1:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.90,1:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.71,1:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do any better?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.71,1:14:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.19,1:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.38,1:14:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to go to church to worship God?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.38,1:14:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to go to church to worship God?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.05,1:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To work with God?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.55,1:14:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To worship God.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.05,1:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.05,1:14:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's an embellishment.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.05,1:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an indication of the degree of sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.76,1:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to a certain degree, you're like
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.97,1:14:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,imploring divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.07,1:14:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,through your own dedication
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.77,1:14:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.14,1:15:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. We recently went
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.57,1:15:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to a lovely church for a very formal
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.65,1:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,occasion. There were a thousand
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.14,1:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,people at the church
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.63,1:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and two wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.89,1:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,bishops.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.06,1:15:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two bishops. We had a
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.22,1:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful time with the bishops and with the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.98,1:15:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,congregation and with the beautiful
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.78,1:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,cathedral and the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.53,1:15:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stained glass windows and the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.26,1:15:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,totality of the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.15,1:15:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.78,1:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have your picture too?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.97,1:15:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.22,1:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gary and Marisha Schreiber.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.42,1:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They're up in
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.68,1:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,D.C. B.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.38,1:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gary and Marisha
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.42,1:15:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Schneider.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.09,1:15:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to AA and they met at our group.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.51,1:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.27,1:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Way back when we were at
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.52,1:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Creative Life Center.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.44,1:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.51,1:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.69,1:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We get e-mails from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.15,1:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you better be careful when you
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.31,1:16:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,start coming to these meetings single.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.23,1:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, you're married.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.06,1:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.21,1:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.98,1:16:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.86,1:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan. Hi, Dr. Mollis.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.02,1:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.31,1:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I wanted to say with what you said
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.64,1:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,about the cookies and the cookie store
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.18,1:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that the cookie monster in me is in heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.59,1:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.90,1:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was here in January and told you that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.94,1:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, will be moving very soon to India.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.25,1:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To India?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.32,1:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,India. I'm going to be staying at Ramana
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.32,1:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maharshi's.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.82,1:16:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's south of Ohio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.47,1:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit. Yeah. A little west.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.44,1:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be staying where?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.44,1:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At Ramana Maharshi's ashram.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.28,1:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.86,1:16:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And very possibly will have an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.44,1:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve as a missionary with Mother
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.44,1:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa's organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.52,1:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So that leads to a question and a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.36,1:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Question of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.01,1:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The question would be as far as vows.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.17,1:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are vows which would be
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.94,1:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,asked of me if I want to join the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.63,1:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,missionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.36,1:17:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty, chastity, obedience, and
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.28,1:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,wholehearted service to the poorest of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.47,1:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the poor.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.10,1:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.56,1:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with taking
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.02,1:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,those vows?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.26,1:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in the highest good, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.30,1:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,altruistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.92,1:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Another friend made a vow, altruistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.27,1:17:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's altruistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.57,1:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.77,1:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay to take those vows?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.68,1:17:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've said at times, I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.07,1:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to take vows, you know, don't take vows.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.35,1:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.73,1:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.46,1:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be appropriate for him to take
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.50,1:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,these vows with Ramana Maharshi's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.52,1:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ashram, is this for you at this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.18,1:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.55,1:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.02,1:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, since this is or could be the last
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.98,1:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,time I get to be in your presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.51,1:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,based on what you said earlier today,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.63,1:18:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,too, would it be okay if first you said
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.71,1:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to tip Jesus on the way?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.63,1:18:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a little tip.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.68,1:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And since it's my tip to Jesus, to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.18,1:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.14,1:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.36,1:18:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He passes on the root of all evil to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.46,1:18:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's in God we trust, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.72,1:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But it says in God we trust on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.27,1:18:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.97,1:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.25,1:18:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a certain place I put such things, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.67,1:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay if I look into your eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.02,1:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold your hand, possibly one last time
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.85,1:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime, to see divinity reflecting back?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.39,1:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to hold your hand and get a blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.56,1:18:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,from you as he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.39,1:18:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes his journey on to life, onward into his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.31,1:18:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His journey onward where?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.36,1:18:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.71,1:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to India and maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.39,1:19:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To Ramana Maharishi's ashram?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.09,1:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.47,1:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe working with Mother Teresa's ashram.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.06,1:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some, over the last year, some very high.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.57,1:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a spiritual idealist.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.52,1:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.14,1:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.97,1:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.22,1:19:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a spiritual idealist.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.57,1:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.77,1:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And may your dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.64,1:19:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.42,1:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.84,1:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got cold hands, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.50,1:19:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He does, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.93,1:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets cold hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.57,1:19:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.42,1:19:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets his cold hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.52,1:19:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be the meeting hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.14,1:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're up here on stage and it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.96,1:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.50,1:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.93,1:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.48,1:19:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.67,1:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to wish you guys much happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.85,1:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and many, many blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.77,1:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, what's the difference
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.71,1:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,between an archangel and an angel
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.21,1:20:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and why an archangel calibrates so much happiness?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.63,1:20:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that an archangel calibrates so much happiness?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.27,1:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.34,1:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hierarchy, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.72,1:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.71,1:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.17,1:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.06,1:20:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, obviously, a bishop would be higher than a clergyman
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.85,1:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and a cardinal would be higher than a bishop.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.15,1:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess, and the pope would be higher than a cardinal.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.93,1:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just rank and order as a human custom, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.02,1:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.23,1:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I was going to ask you,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.43,1:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could bless these for my four children
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.52,1:20:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and bless this book.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.89,1:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never read any of your books,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.34,1:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know all about them
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.11,1:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because I have a dear friend that would read them to me
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.72,1:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then explain them to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.46,1:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.19,1:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to me, they're very hard reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.92,1:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe you could put a little spell on this
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.38,1:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that I could read this myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.60,1:21:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what she's asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.56,1:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to bless the...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.89,1:21:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.05,1:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The little bracelets for her children.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.39,1:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And bless the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.67,1:21:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get them all in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.89,1:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.52,1:21:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.35,1:21:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.98,1:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.85,1:21:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.64,1:21:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put your hand on here and bless it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.43,1:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless these beads in thy name, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.98,1:21:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.77,1:21:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.17,1:21:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because those are going to your children and in the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.89,1:21:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.28,1:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.06,1:21:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.43,1:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.78,1:21:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.36,1:21:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.55,1:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.97,1:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.06,1:21:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He does that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.56,1:21:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our bird does it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.75,1:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our bird goes,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.67,1:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.10,1:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.09,1:21:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.48,1:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.43,1:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my African great parrot says,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.89,1:22:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.52,1:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum, bum, bum, bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.60,1:22:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.57,1:22:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.46,1:22:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.42,1:22:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.47,1:22:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.47,1:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Mary,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.57,1:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and I really just wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.47,1:22:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for the teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.43,1:22:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way they've changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.34,1:22:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really just wanted to spend a few moments
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.64,1:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in your presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.38,1:22:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to give you both a hug,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.06,1:22:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know that that's not really allowed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.30,1:22:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So could I get a hug from you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.82,1:22:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and a blessing from you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.22,1:22:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come over here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.60,1:22:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.01,1:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.75,1:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.07,1:22:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.56,1:22:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.47,1:22:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.19,1:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.98,1:22:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are indeed beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.71,1:22:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.36,1:22:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.39,1:22:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.36,1:22:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want him silent?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.10,1:22:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.56,1:22:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.00,1:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.06,1:23:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.65,1:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.00,1:23:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very, very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.30,1:23:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.88,1:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 4 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.11,1:23:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have to stop at 4.30,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.02,1:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can go into the 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.50,1:23:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then do our ending if you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.34,1:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, 20 minutes, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.30,1:23:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.94,1:23:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This arm is feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.93,1:23:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.00,1:23:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.02,1:23:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.69,1:23:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.61,1:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.72,1:23:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.56,1:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fourth time here,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.57,1:23:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time I think
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.42,1:23:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you a question,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.72,1:23:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I look into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.72,1:23:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.14,1:23:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.82,1:23:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.97,1:23:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And during the lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.56,1:24:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you said you liked coffee ice cream,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.43,1:24:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I heard toffee ice cream,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.97,1:24:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so I got you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.69,1:24:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got one.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.48,1:24:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's caramel sutra.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.75,1:24:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.13,1:24:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he loves that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.02,1:24:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Caramel sutra.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.35,1:24:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.02,1:24:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And on one of your videos,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.56,1:24:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in handling my major crisis,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.23,1:24:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that you were making
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.02,1:24:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,chicken livers for your cat,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.19,1:24:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.07,1:24:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you transcended the belief system
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.19,1:24:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,about how you can't eat chicken livers.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.50,1:24:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I got you chicken livers, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.61,1:24:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a lot of ice in here,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.84,1:24:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm willing to carry it to your car,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.22,1:24:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to your house.
